Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}美洲狮，太低了{\r}\NWe're too low, Cougar
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}加大动力{\r}\NIncrease power Some more power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}请进{\r}\NCome in
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}长官{\r}\NSir
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}美洲狮，你应该在医护室的 你在想什么？{\r}\NCougar, you should be in sickbay.What's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我的妻儿{\r}\NMy wife and kid, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}他今天几乎变成孤儿 我从没见过他{\r}\NI almost orphaned him today, and I've never even seen him
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我不知道发生了什么事 但是我很害怕{\r}\NI don't know what happened up there, but I was so scared
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}别这样 我们以前也见过这种事{\r}\N-Come on, we've seen this before
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}不，长官{\r}\N-No, sir
