Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我已经受够了，对不起，长官{\r}\NI've lost the edge I'm sorry, sir I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}美洲狮{\r}\NCougar
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.66,0:13:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}谢谢，马华力{\r}\NThanks, Maverick
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}马华力、野鹅，进来{\r}\NMaverick, Goose, come in here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.43,0:13:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}- 发生了什么事？ - 我不知道{\r}\N-What the hell's going on?  -I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.62,0:13:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}马华力，你刚才做的事很勇敢{\r}\NMaverick, you just did an incredibly brave thing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}可是你应该做的是降落{\r}\NWhat you should have done was land your plane
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.42,0:14:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}战机是纳税人的，不是你的{\r}\NYou don't own that plane, the taxpayers do
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你真是狂妄自大{\r}\NSon, your ego is writing checks your body can't cash
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你试过被开除 失去当小组队长的资格三次{\r}\NYou've been busted.You lost your qualifications as section leader three times
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我两次帮你恢复职位{\r}\NPut in hack twice by me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你却试过高速 飞过控制塔和上将之女{\r}\NWith a history of high-speed passes over five air-control towers and one admiral's daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}班萍妮？{\r}\NPenny Benjamin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}- 你这笨蛋能在这儿真是走运 - 谢谢{\r}\N-And you, asshole You're lucky to be here  -Thank you, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}别再说废话，马华力 你的家人不是空军中最好的{\r}\NLet's not bullshit, Maverick,your family name ain't the best in the Navy
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你应该比他做得更好 你究竟在想什么？{\r}\NYou need to be doing it better and cleaner than the other guy. Now, what is it with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.12,0:14:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我只想为国效力 当最好的海军战机师{\r}\NJust wanna serve my country,be the best fighter pilot in Navy, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}马华力，别骗我了{\r}\NDon't screw around with me, Maverick
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你全凭直觉当机师 而且很出色{\r}\NYou're a hell of an instinctive pilot Maybe too good
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我很想开除你 不过我有另一个麻烦{\r}\NI'd like to bust your butt, but I can't.I got another problem here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我要从队中派人去米拉马{\r}\NI gotta send somebody from this squadron to Miramar
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我要做一些事 我难以置信的事{\r}\NI gotta do something here.I still can't believe it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我要让你梦想成真 派你去面对一流的海军{\r}\NI gotta give you your dream shot.I'm gonna send you up against the best
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你们两个会进顶级机师部{\r}\NYou two characters are going to Top Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.78,0:15:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你们会和世上的顶级机师 交手五星期{\r}\NFor five weeks,you're gonna fly against the best fighter pilots in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你是第二，美洲狮是第一{\r}\NYou were number two, Cougar was number one
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}美洲狮放弃开战机{\r}\NCougar lost it, turned in his wings
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你们就成了第一{\r}\NYou guys are number one
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}记着一件事 你们闯过这么多祸{\r}\NBut you remember one thing: You screw up just this much,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}迟早会被调往运送狗屎的{\r}\Nyou'll be flying a cargo plane full of rubber dog shit out of Hong Kong
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}是，长官{\r}\NYes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}没事了{\r}\NThat is all
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}改天把米格机的事告诉我{\r}\NYou can tell me about the MiG some other time
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}两位{\r}\NGentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}祝你们好运{\r}\N-Good luck, gentlemen  -Thank you, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}谢谢{\r}\NThank you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}（美国空军基地 加州米拉马）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}海军在韩战的杀敌比率 是十二比一{\r}\NDuring Korea, the Navy kill ratio was 12-to-1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我们一架战机 就能击落敌人十二架{\r}\NWe shot down 12 of their jets for every one of ours
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}到了越战时比率降至三比一{\r}\NDuring Vietnam, that ratio fell to 3-to-1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我们的机师太依赖导弹了{\r}\NOur pilots become dependent upon missiles
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}他们失去了一些空战技巧{\r}\NThey had lost some of their dogfighting skills
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}成立顶级机师部 是为了教导你们空战策略{\r}\NTop Gun was created to teach ACM: Air Combat Maneuvering
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}也就是空中格斗{\r}\NDogfighting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.41,0:16:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}真令人兴奋{\r}\NThis gives me a hard-on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}到了越战末期 比率回升至十二比一{\r}\NBy the end of Vietnam, that ratio was back up to 12-to-1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}别跟我开玩笑{\r}\N-Don't tease me
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}请下窗帘{\r}\N-Blinds, please
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我想藉着这次机会 介绍指挥官给大家认识{\r}\NI'd like to take this opportunity to introduce you to our commanding officer at Top Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.73,0:16:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}他是第一位获得 顶级机师奖的人{\r}\NThe very first man to win the Top Gun trophy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你不会在其他地方找到 比他更优秀的机师了{\r}\NYou will not find a finer fighter pilot anywhere in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}麦米克长官，外号毒蛇{\r}\NCommander Mike Metcalf Callsign: Viper
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.57,0:17:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}各位{\r}\NGentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你们是海军空战人员中 最好的百分之一{\r}\NYou are the top one percent of all naval aviators
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.11,0:17:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}是精英，精英中之精英{\r}\NThe elite The best of the best
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我们会令你们更进一步{\r}\NWe'll make you better
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.05,0:17:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你们每天至少 要执行两项空中任务{\r}\NYou'll fly at least two combat missions a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}当中要上课 听取自己表现所得到的评价{\r}\Nattend classes in between and evaluations of your performance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你们在每次的空中任务 都要面对新挑战{\r}\NOn each combat sequence, you're gonna meet a different challenge
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}每一次都会更加困难{\r}\NEvery encounter is gonna be much more difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我们会教你们 令F14尽展所长{\r}\NWe're gonna teach you to fly the F-14 right to the edge of the envelope,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你们会比以前开得更快{\r}\Nfaster than you've ever flown before
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}也会更加危险{\r}\Nand more dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}各位，我们不是在这儿立法{\r}\NNow, we don't make policy here, gentlemen
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.14,0:17:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}立法是由获选的官员 和平民做的{\r}\NElected officials, civilians do that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我们只是这些政策的工具{\r}\NWe are the instruments of that policy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}虽然我们不是在打仗 但要假装是{\r}\NAnd although we're not at war,we must always act as though we are at war
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你在做什么？{\r}\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我只是在想谁是最一流的机师{\r}\N-The tip of the spear best be sharp  -I'm just wondering who's the best
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你们可能会想 谁是最一流的机师{\r}\NIn case some of you wonder who the best is,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}他们的名字就在墙上的板子上{\r}\Nthey're up here on this plaque on the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}最佳机师和他的通讯员的名字 都会记录在上面{\r}\NThe best driver and his RIO from each class has his name on it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.87,0:18:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}他们可以选择回来当教官{\r}\NAnd they have the option to come back here to be Top Gun instructors
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你认为你的名字会在上面？{\r}\NYou think your name's gonna be on that plaque?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}是，长官{\r}\NYes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你真自大，周围有这么多人{\r}\NThat's pretty arrogant, considering the company you're in
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}是，长官{\r}\NYes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我喜欢机师自大{\r}\NI like that in a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}记着，离开这儿后 我们都是同一队人{\r}\NJust remember, when it's over out there,we're all on the same team
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.20,0:18:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}各位，这儿是教大家战斗的{\r}\NGentlemen, this school is about combat
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.97,0:18:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}当第二是没意思的{\r}\NThere are no points for second place
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}解散{\r}\NDismissed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.97,0:18:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}做得好{\r}\NNice going
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.01,0:18:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}后补者的徽章在女洗手间{\r}\NThe plaque for the alternates is down in the ladies' room
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.32,0:19:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}天啊，真是笑死我了{\r}\NOh, Jesus Oh, you kill me You really do
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}不，“野鹅” 是两个O的{\r}\NNo, no, no There's two O's in "Goose", boys
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}真是一个不愁没目标的环境{\r}\NThis is what I call a target-rich environment
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你在两腿之间生活{\r}\NYou live your life between your legs, Mav
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}野鹅，连你也可以来这儿{\r}\NGoose, even you could get laid in a place like this
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}能找到说脏话的女孩 我就高兴了{\r}\NI'm telling you, I'd be happy to find a girl who'd talk dirty to me
