Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.70,0:35:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}两位，你们第一天过得真充实{\r}\NGentlemen You had a hell of a first day
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.70,0:35:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}这次任务的假设地面是一万英尺{\r}\NThe hard deck for this hop was 10000 feet
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.07,0:35:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你们明知故犯{\r}\NYou knew it, you broke it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.11,0:35:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}希军官不见了你们之后 你们跟着他低飞{\r}\NYou followed Commander Heatherly below after he lost sight of you and called no joy
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.68,0:35:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}为什么？{\r}\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.15,0:35:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}长官，我看到希军官{\r}\NSir I had Commander Heatherly in my sights.He saw me move in for the kill
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.26,0:35:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}他看到我飞到开火的位置 就飞低过假设地面{\r}\NHe then proceeded below the hard deck
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.96,0:35:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我们只有几秒低飞了{\r}\NWe weren't below 10000 for more than a few seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.56,0:35:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我瞄准了他 见没有危险就开火{\r}\NI had the shot, there was no danger, so I took it
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.97,0:36:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你开了火，你破坏了重要守则{\r}\NYou took it And broke a major rule of engagement
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.97,0:36:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}飞越控制塔时又犯了另一条{\r}\NThen you broke another one with that circus-stunt flyby
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.28,0:36:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}麦上尉{\r}\NLieutenant Mitchell, Top Gun rules of engagement exist
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.65,0:36:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}守则是为了你 和队员的安全而设立的{\r}\Nfor your safety and for that of your team
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.75,0:36:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}守则不可随时更改，我也是{\r}\NThey are not flexible, nor am I
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.02,0:36:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}不遵守的话就要被开除 清楚了吗？{\r}\NEither obey them or you're history.Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.16,0:36:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}是，长官{\r}\NYes, sir
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.14,0:36:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}解散{\r}\NDismissed
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.18,0:36:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我真的很享受那一下，谢谢你{\r}\NI really enjoyed that, Mav, thanks a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.68,0:36:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}天啊{\r}\NHoly shit
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.69,0:36:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我或者可以学习当货车司机{\r}\NMaybe I could learn how to be a truck driver
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.02,0:36:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你有货车驾驶学校的电话号码{\r}\NMav, you have the number of that truck-driving school we saw on TV?Truck Master, I think it is
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.99,0:36:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我可能会需要到{\r}\NI might need that
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.60,0:37:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}评估报告已经显示了他很飘忽{\r}\NHis fitness report says it all.He's a wild card
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.47,0:37:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}他靠直觉开战机 完全无法预测{\r}\NFlies by the seat of his pants.Completely unpredictable
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.57,0:37:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}- 他吓倒你了？ - 是{\r}\N-He got you, didn't he?  -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.11,0:37:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}马华力，我曾经和他爸爸共事{\r}\NMaverick I flew with his old man
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.85,0:37:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}告诉我 你想和他一起上战场吗？{\r}\NTell me one thing.If you had to go into battle, would you want him with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.42,0:37:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我不知道{\r}\NI don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.39,0:37:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我真的不知道{\r}\NI just don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.77,0:37:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}还没睡吗？{\r}\N-You still awake? 
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.74,0:37:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}是{\r}\N -Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.64,0:37:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你在想什么？{\r}\NWhat's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.71,0:37:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}睡不着{\r}\NCan't sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.85,0:37:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我知道可以进顶级机师部时 我只想拿机师奖{\r}\NYou know, when I first realized that we were going to Top Gun, all I could think about was getting that trophy
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.62,0:38:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我要坦白跟你说{\r}\NI gotta be straight with you, Mav
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.13,0:38:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我现在只希望我们能毕业{\r}\NRight now, I just hope we graduate
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.66,0:38:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我有家人 我不能浪费这个机会{\r}\NI got a family to think about.I can't afford to blow this
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.04,0:38:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}其实飞越控制塔不算什么{\r}\NYeah, I guess that flyby wasn't such a big hit
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.51,0:38:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我知道你很难受{\r}\NLook, man, I know it's tough for you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.15,0:38:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}他们因为你是麦杜克的儿子 而不让你进海军学院{\r}\NThey wouldn't let you in the academy because you're Duke Mitchell's kid
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.92,0:38:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你要承受这个污名{\r}\NYou have to live with that reputation
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.42,0:38:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我们每次飞行时 你都像在面对鬼魂一样{\r}\NBut it's like every time we go up there,it's like you're flying against a ghost
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.46,0:38:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你令我紧张{\r}\NIt makes me nervous
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.20,0:38:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我只有你这个亲人{\r}\NYou're the only family I've got
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.90,0:38:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我不会令你失望的，我保证{\r}\NI'm not gonna let you down I promise you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.02,0:38:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}出去吧{\r}\NGet out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.60,0:39:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}在这情形下 倒转打转会很有效{\r}\NA rolling reversal would work well in that situation
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.07,0:39:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}如果我十字形倒转飞 就能马上转为发炮{\r}\NIf I reversed on a hard cross,I could immediately go to guns on them
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.24,0:39:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}在这种速度下，太快了{\r}\NYeah, but at that speed, it's too fast
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.75,0:39:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}而且太过急进{\r}\NIt's a little bit too aggressive
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.85,0:39:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}太过急进？{\r}\NToo aggressive
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.72,0:39:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我觉得应该这样做就这样做{\r}\NYeah, I guess when I see something,I go right after it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.29,0:39:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你没告诉我你那晚去了哪儿{\r}\NYou didn't tell me who you were the other night
