Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.70,0:39:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你应有此报{\r}\NYou deserved it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.93,0:39:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我知道 不过有人想你约我吃晚餐{\r}\NI know But you were tempted to ask me out for dinner
