Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.41,0:40:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}- 不？ - 我不和学员约会{\r}\NNo I don't date students
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.05,0:40:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我看得出这对你很危险{\r}\NI can see it's dangerous for you
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.66,0:40:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}但是如果政府相信我 你也可以{\r}\NBut if the government trusts me, maybe you could
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.00,0:40:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}这不只是花式飞行这么简单{\r}\NIt takes a lot more than just fancy flying
