Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.59,0:41:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good Come on
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.53,0:41:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, now
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.47,0:41:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Mav, 4-7 Let's get them.Those guys are animals
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.21,0:41:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.58,0:41:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good serve, good serve
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.21,0:42:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's game
