Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.02,0:42:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}马华力，再打一局 就追成平手了{\r}\NMav Mav Come on, man.Just one more game That evens it up
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.16,0:42:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我们很大机会会赢的 我们有实力{\r}\N-Come on, we can take them  -No
