Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.33,0:42:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}办事？只是再打一局而已{\r}\NTake care of? Just one more game
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.80,0:42:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}- 为了我好吗？ - 对不起{\r}\N-Please? For me?  -I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.80,0:42:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你应该内疚，来吧{\r}\NYou're sorry Come on -Mother Goose, you pussy!  -For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.41,0:43:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}该死{\r}\NDamn it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.79,0:43:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}上尉{\r}\NLieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.19,0:43:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}不唱歌了吗？{\r}\NWhat, no singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.50,0:43:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}- 我... - 不用道歉{\r}\N-Look, I'm--I'm-- -No apologies
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.17,0:43:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你不介意的话 我想去快快洗一个澡{\r}\NIf you don't mind, I'm--I'm gonna just take a quick shower
