Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.40,0:44:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}狐狸，他是个聪明人{\r}\NYou know, Charlie, he's a smart guy
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.60,0:44:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}为什么不干脆告诉他 请他来的目的？{\r}\NWhy don't you just tell him why you've got him here"
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.64,0:44:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}是什么？{\r}\NWell?
