Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.19,0:44:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我正在努力工作 希望能够升职{\r}\NI'm trying for this big promotion at work, and if I get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.95,0:44:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}成功的话，我不会再留在这儿{\r}\NI'm not gonna be here much longer
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.76,0:44:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你似乎什么都想清楚了{\r}\NIt seems to me you've got it all figured out
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.03,0:44:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}是{\r}\NYeah
