Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.97,0:44:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}对不起{\r}\NSorry
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.87,0:44:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你常常如愿以偿？{\r}\NYou always get what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.47,0:45:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}不...可能是吧{\r}\NNo, not always Yeah, maybe
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.88,0:45:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}那就别这么在意那架米格机{\r}\NThen relax about the MiG
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.06,0:45:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}这首音乐...{\r}\NThis music
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.63,0:45:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}是老朋友的？{\r}\NAn old friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.47,0:45:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我父母很喜欢这首音乐{\r}\NMy folks loved it
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.74,0:45:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我有很多年没听过了{\r}\NI haven't heard this in years
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.61,0:45:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}妈妈以前在房里 叫我把它不停重播{\r}\NMy mother used to call down from her room and have me play this over and over again
