Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.33,0:45:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}他死后不久她也死了{\r}\NShe died shortly after him
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.90,0:45:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你爸爸怎样死的？{\r}\NWhat happened to your father?
