Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.45,0:46:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我还没知道得这么深入{\r}\NWell, I didn't get that far
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.49,0:46:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}这是一个谜{\r}\NWell, it's a big mystery
