Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.07,0:46:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我爸爸是很优秀的机师{\r}\NMy old man was a great fighter pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.08,0:46:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}但谁知道呢？ 一切都被列作机密资料{\r}\NBut who the hell knows?It's all classified
