Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.47,1:13:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}天啊，他很喜欢和你并肩作战{\r}\NGod, he loved flying with you, Maverick
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.56,1:13:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}就算没遇上你，他也会当机师{\r}\NBut he'd have flown anyway without you
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.49,1:13:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}虽然他会讨厌这种事 但他还是会做{\r}\NHe'd have hated it, but he would've done it
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.15,1:14:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我们发现这架F14的引擎 卷进了气流{\r}\NWe find that the F-14 flat spin was induced by the disruption of airflow into the starboard engine
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.49,1:14:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}这种干扰令引擎 出现过多的偏航率{\r}\NThis disruption stalled the engine,which produced enough yaw rate
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.97,1:14:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}结果令机身不停打转 无法修正{\r}\Nto induce a spin which was unrecoverable
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.10,1:14:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}这种问题 不是麦上尉可察觉到的{\r}\NThere was no way Lieutenant Mitchell could either see or avoid the jet wash which produced the engine stall
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.91,1:14:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}所以资询会发现{\r}\NTherefore, the board of inquiry finds that Lieutenant Pete Mitchell
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.95,1:14:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}麦彼得上尉 并没在7月29日的意外犯错{\r}\Nwas not at fault in the accident of 29 July
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.55,1:14:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}这次的意外 不会记在麦上尉的纪录上{\r}\NLieutenant Mitchell's record will be cleared of this incident
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.35,1:14:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}麦上尉马上复职{\r}\NLieutenant Mitchell is restored to flight status without further delay
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.96,1:14:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}调查完毕{\r}\NThese proceedings are closed
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.03,1:14:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}尽快让他回复飞行{\r}\NGet him up flying, soon
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.23,1:15:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}小子，快点进战场{\r}\NCome on, kid, come on Get in there Engage
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.33,1:15:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}马华力，东北方有一架敌机{\r}\NAll right, you got a bogey at 2 o'clock low, Maverick
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.67,1:15:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你的位置很好 简直是轻而易举{\r}\NYou got the angle Piece of cake, pal
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.54,1:15:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}快开火，小子{\r}\NTake the shot, kid Take the shot
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.34,1:15:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}马华力，你随时都可以加入{\r}\NYou can engage any time, Maverick
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.32,1:15:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你要去哪儿？{\r}\NHey, where the hell are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.79,1:15:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}情况不妙{\r}\NIt's not good It doesn't look good
Dialogue: 0,1:15:52.36,1:15:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}情况不妙是什么意思？ 情况好到不得了{\r}\NWhat do you mean, it doesn't look good?It doesn't get to look any better than that
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.21,1:16:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你本来可以击中他的 我们可以击中他的{\r}\NHey, man, we could've had him.Hey, we could've had him, man!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.45,1:16:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我准备好时自然会发炮{\r}\NI will fire when I am goddamn good and ready!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.62,1:16:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你明白了吗？{\r}\NYou got that?!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.97,1:16:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}他仍然未回复过来 他不愿战斗{\r}\NHe can't get back in the saddle Won't engage
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.91,1:16:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}只过了几天{\r}\NIt's only been a few days
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.38,1:16:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}他可能不能回复过来{\r}\NYou know, he just might not make it back
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.05,1:16:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep sending him up
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.27,1:17:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}麦彼得{\r}\NMitchell
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.91,1:17:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我很难过野鹅死了{\r}\NI'm sorry about Goose
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.85,1:17:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}大家都喜欢他{\r}\NEverybody liked him
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.32,1:17:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我很难过{\r}\NI'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.44,1:17:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你好，我是人狼{\r}\NHi, it's Wolfman
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.31,1:17:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}马华力刚刚退学了{\r}\NYeah, Maverick just quit
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.81,1:18:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}对不起{\r}\NExcuse me
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.08,1:18:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我可以坐下吗？{\r}\NMay I?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.81,1:18:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}随便{\r}\NPlease
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.85,1:18:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}和他要的一样{\r}\NI'll have what he's having
Dialogue: 0,1:18:36.93,1:18:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}是毒药吧{\r}\NHemlock, is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.79,1:18:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}是冰水{\r}\NIce water
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.17,1:18:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你不和我道别吗？{\r}\NYou weren't gonna say goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.41,1:18:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}听说你得到华盛顿的工作了{\r}\NI heard you got that job in Washington
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.41,1:18:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}恭喜{\r}\N Congratulations
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.28,1:18:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}谢谢{\r}\NThanks
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.68,1:19:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}但是我不会不辞而别{\r}\NBut I wasn't gonna leave without saying goodbye
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.42,1:19:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}看到你真好{\r}\NIt's good to see you
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.22,1:19:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}谢谢{\r}\NThanks
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.59,1:19:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你要去哪儿？{\r}\NWhere you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.40,1:19:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你连机票也没有吧{\r}\NYou don't even have a ticket, do you?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.03,1:19:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我看过所有证据 这不是你的责任{\r}\NListen, I've seen all the evidence,and it's not your responsibility
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.01,1:19:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}不是你的错 你是海军里的精英{\r}\NIt's not your fault You're one of the best pilots in the Navy
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.11,1:19:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你在高空战斗是很危险{\r}\NWhat you do up there, it's dangerous
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.68,1:19:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}但是你得继续下去{\r}\NBut you've got to go on
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.02,1:19:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你不明白{\r}\NYou don't understand
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.89,1:19:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我刚认识你时 你的生活很充实{\r}\NWhen I first met you, you were larger than life
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.20,1:19:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}看看你{\r}\NLook at you
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.57,1:19:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你不过步伐急速的生活 你不会快乐{\r}\NYou're not gonna be happy unless you're going Mach 2 with your hair on fire,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.94,1:19:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你知道的{\r}\N-you know that  -No, it's over
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.87,1:20:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}不，完了 做精英中的精英{\r}\N-It's just over  -To be the best of the best
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.68,1:20:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}就是犯错后仍然继续努力{\r}\Nmeans you make mistakes and then you go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.75,1:20:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}这对大家来说都一样{\r}\NIt's just like the rest of us
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.25,1:20:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你以为我不知道吗？{\r}\NYou don't think I know that?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.42,1:20:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我是来帮你的{\r}\NI'm here to help
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.02,1:20:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}谢谢你{\r}\NLook, thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.86,1:20:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我想别人帮我的话 自然会开口{\r}\NBut if I wanted help, really,I would have asked for it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.10,1:20:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}原来我来迟了{\r}\NSo I'm too late
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.41,1:20:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你已经离开了{\r}\NYou've already left
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.54,1:20:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你什么都没学到{\r}\NYou didn't learn a damn thing, did you?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.81,1:20:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你只学会退缩{\r}\NExcept to quit
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.02,1:20:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你真的很擅长做这种事呢{\r}\NYou've got that maneuver down real well
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.76,1:20:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}再见了，麦彼得{\r}\NSo long, Pete Mitchell
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.03,1:21:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你好，马华力，请进{\r}\NWell, hi, Maverick, come on in
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.49,1:21:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}- 你好吗？ - 我很好{\r}\N-How are you doing?  -Good
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.80,1:21:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}- 真的，你真的没事？ - 我很好{\r}\N-Really? You sure you're feeling okay?  -Oh, I feel great
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.50,1:21:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}- 珍美，你要喝点什么吗？ - 不必了{\r}\NJamie, come on.Can I get you a drink or anything else like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.26,1:21:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}请随便坐，米克马上就下来了{\r}\N-No, thank you  -Okay, well, why don't you just make yourself comfortable Mike will be right down
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.97,1:21:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}谢谢{\r}\NGreat, thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.39,1:22:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你爸爸和我在奥利士卡尼号的 VF51小队并肩作战{\r}\NI flew with your old man VF-51, the Oriskany
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.77,1:22:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你真的很像他{\r}\NYou're a lot like he was Only better and worse
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.04,1:22:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}他是一个天生的英雄主义者{\r}\NHe was a natural heroic son of a bitch, that one
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.68,1:22:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}他真的没做错{\r}\NSo he did do it right
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.99,1:22:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}是的，他没做错{\r}\NYeah, he did it right
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.17,1:22:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}所以你这样开战机？ 你想证明什么？{\r}\NIs that why you fly the way you do?Trying to prove something?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.51,1:22:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你爸爸的确没做错{\r}\NYeah, your old man did it right
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.58,1:22:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我要告诉你的事是机密事件 可能会令我丢掉工作{\r}\NWhat I'm about to tell you is classified.It could end my career
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.52,1:22:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我们置身于一场 我梦寐以求的战斗之中{\r}\NWe were in the worst dogfight I ever dreamed of
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.89,1:23:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}敌机像萤火虫般布满天空{\r}\NBogies like fireflies all over the sky
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.76,1:23:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}他的F4战机被击中，他受了伤{\r}\NHis F-4 was hit, he was wounded,but he could've made it back
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.36,1:23:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}他本来可以回基地 但是他留在战场{\r}\NHe stayed in it, saved three planes 
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.70,1:23:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}在坠毁之前救了三架战机{\r}\Nbefore he bought it
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.07,1:23:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我怎么会从没听说过？{\r}\NHow come I never heard that before?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.60,1:23:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}州政府不会告诉家属{\r}\NThat's not something the State Department tells dependents
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.04,1:23:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}因为地图出错而发生战事{\r}\Nwhen the battle occurred over the wrong line on some map
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.58,1:23:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}- 你当时在场？ - 是{\r}\N-So you were there?  -I was there
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.92,1:23:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你在想什么？{\r}\NWhat's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.99,1:23:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我的选择{\r}\NMy options, sir
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.12,1:23:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}很简单{\r}\NSimple
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.42,1:23:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你已经拿到足够分数 出席明天的毕业礼{\r}\NFirst, you've acquired enough points to show up tomorrow and graduate with your Top Gun class
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.23,1:23:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}否则就退学{\r}\NOr you can quit
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.37,1:23:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}这不是丢脸的事 那样打转我也会被吓倒{\r}\NThere'd be no disgrace That spin was hell.It would've shook me up
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.37,1:23:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你认为我应该退学？{\r}\NSo you think I should quit?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.31,1:23:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我没说过{\r}\NI didn't say that
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.68,1:23:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你觉得是你害了野鹅 而且有信心危机{\r}\NThe simple fact is, you feel responsible for Goose,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.65,1:24:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我不会坐在这儿跟你说好话{\r}\NNow, I'm not gonna sit here and blow sunshine up your ass, lieutenant
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.09,1:24:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}一个好机师必须评估发生的事{\r}\NA good pilot is compelled to always evaluate what's happened
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.52,1:24:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}这样才能学以致用{\r}\NSo he can apply what he's learned
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.19,1:24:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}到了高空我们就要全力以赴 这是我们的职责{\r}\NUp there, we gotta push it That's our job
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.44,1:24:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}上尉，这全看你的选择{\r}\NIt's your option, lieutenant, all yours
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.18,1:24:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}对不起，在周日打扰你{\r}\NSorry to bother you on a Sunday, sir,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.75,1:24:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}谢谢你抽空见我{\r}\Nbut thank you very much for your time
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.12,1:24:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}不要紧，祝你好运{\r}\NNo problem Good luck
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.69,1:24:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}（房子出租）{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.91,1:25:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}各位{\r}\N-Gentlemen  
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.34,1:25:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}马华力在哪儿？{\r}\N-Where's Maverick?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.71,1:25:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}我不知道他在哪儿{\r}\NI don't know where he is
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.68,1:25:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}你知道他有什么打算吗？{\r}\NYou know what he's planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.55,1:25:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}他一定是很难过{\r}\NGotta be hard on the guy, though
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.45,1:26:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}恭喜{\r}\NCongratulations
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.29,1:26:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}谢谢{\r}\NThank you
Dialogue: 0,1:26:20.89,1:26:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}- 恭喜 - 谢谢{\r}\N-Congratulations  -Thanks, Mav
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.29,1:26:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}长官{\r}\NSir
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.43,1:26:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24\fn黑体}各位{\r}\NGentlemen
